com.labjack

Class LJM.Constants

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.labjack.LJM.Constants
  • Enclosing class:
    LJM

    public class LJM.Constants
extends java.lang.Object
    Constants is a class containing the constants from the LJM library. The "LJM_" prefix have been removed from the original names.
